sequenceDiagram
    title STATISTICAL TRAJECTORY PREDICTOR
    actor Student
    participant Analytics
    participant RouteManager
    participant TrajectoryPredictor
    participant Supabase

    Student ->> Analytics: Opens Analytics
    Analytics ->> RouteManager:API request to retrieve past predicted grades
    RouteManager ->> Supabase: Retrieve past predicted grades
    Supabase -->> RouteManager: Past predicted grades
    RouteManager ->> TrajectoryPredictor: Past predicted grades
    TrajectoryPredictor -->> RouteManager: Final predicted grade and current trajectory
    RouteManager ->> Supabase: Store final predicted grade and current trajectory
    Supabase -->> RouteManager: Confirmation message
    RouteManager -->> Analytics: Final predicted grade and current trajectory
    Analytics ->> Student:Final predicted grade and current trajectory


